description:
Leta's life changed in a fleeting moment when fate led her to a mysterious artifact. Leta was strolling in the mountains near her hometown with her friend Lina, photographing nature, when they stumbled upon an ancient box. Lina decided to take the strange object home â€” after all, it seemed to belong to no one.

Soon after, she vanished without a trace, leaving behind only a photograph and that very box. It's up to Leta to discover the terrifying secrets the artifact holds...

Third-person horror;
Eerie atmosphere;
Unique style and soundtrack;
Vibrant animated characters;
Puzzles;
Roughly two hours of gameplay;
The box.
